1
00:00:06,120 --> 00:00:07,200
Mary!

2
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:09,520
Mangu, don't. Leave me.

3
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:13,120
You mean, Don't leave me?
I'll never leave you. Come on.

4
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:16,120
Mangu, don't. Go away!

5
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:17,280
No way.

6
00:00:17,360 --> 00:00:18,800
This is not the time to go,
but come closer.

7
00:00:18,920 --> 00:00:20,520
Please give me a kiss.
Come on, Maggi. Come on.

8
00:00:20,680 --> 00:00:22,120
Somebody will see us.

9
00:00:22,200 --> 00:00:23,400
No one has seen us
for the past one year.

10
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:24,560
How would anyone see us now?

11
00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:26,120
Please come on.
- No, Mangu.

12
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:27,280
Mangu!
- Who's it?

13
00:00:28,520 --> 00:00:29,600
Mangu!

14
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:31,200
Maggi, how can you..

15
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:35,120
No, sir. Mangu touches me.
He harasses me all the time.

16
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:37,800
No, sir. Whatever she said
in English is all wrong.

17
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:41,000
Sir, if I have done something wrong,
then so has she.

18
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:42,640
We both are in this together.

19
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:44,000
Together?

20
00:00:44,120 --> 00:00:45,680
Sir!
- Let her go!

21
00:00:47,760 --> 00:00:48,840
Let her go!

22
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:51,120
Get out of here.

23
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,280
Having fun, alone!

24
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:57,360
I lost my job
because of this mere thing.

25
00:00:57,720 --> 00:00:59,680
Don't worry. You carry on, please.
